  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/efb8e012f973cba3996151b9679a556b.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/efb8e012f973cba3996151b9679a556b.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>Experience a unique escape room adventure as you play <strong>Mystery Box: The Journey</strong>, where you will encounter a perfect blend of tactile exploration, challenging puzzles, and astonishing environments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the challenge of exploring mysterious locations and solving peculiar riddles, you won't forget the hours spent playing this puzzle adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/824d1fd184b7adb65fd982b33be9f146.poster.avif?t=1770298492\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/824d1fd184b7adb65fd982b33be9f146.webm?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/824d1fd184b7adb65fd982b33be9f146.mp4?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And that's not all! Challenges and fun don't stop after unlocking all the 10 boxes and escaping the location you're trapped in, because you can also play an extra mini-game called The Jackbox, which resembles the classic hangman game and requires you to guess a variety of words to obtain AI-generated wallpapers for your device, making your experience even more satisfying and enjoyable! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an escape room journey through a collection of cunningly complicated boxes filled with enticing enigmas and brainteasers to solve. Each level is full of intricacy and has a portal to a new, stunning environment </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/799bdec1fbbbeeaffe3ab5cdd3620b5b.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/799bdec1fbbbeeaffe3ab5cdd3620b5b.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>Unlock all the achievements and show the community how far you have gone, this will spice up your game experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/37c0fb8b6bce23aeee169a97dac1059b.avif?t=1770298492\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/cae6bdb4fd9df17abec942eb377b132c.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/cae6bdb4fd9df17abec942eb377b132c.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>Its simple user interface makes it easy to dive in but tricky to walk away from. A special blend of captivating escape room puzzles awaits you, ensuring an immersive experience that skillfully balances challenge and entertainment to keep you engaged for hours </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/3071aa32c76e63bcd0b6cbe70cc153a9.poster.avif?t=1770298492\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/3071aa32c76e63bcd0b6cbe70cc153a9.webm?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/3071aa32c76e63bcd0b6cbe70cc153a9.mp4?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/95a9d57231975b2213eaa922cff5d55a.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/95a9d57231975b2213eaa922cff5d55a.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>How many words can you guess in this extra challenge? Insert a token in the Jackbox and find a hidden word within 5 attempts to win an AI-generated wallpaper that you can either save in your device </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/b7d75fa9d32dda7829622a9e21acbb88.poster.avif?t=1770298492\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/b7d75fa9d32dda7829622a9e21acbb88.webm?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/b7d75fa9d32dda7829622a9e21acbb88.mp4?t=1770298492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/54ee9c98c33835c870ca4a603ce0c2ec.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/54ee9c98c33835c870ca4a603ce0c2ec.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with buttons, levers, and particular mechanisms to unlock several parts of the boxes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/3bfff228a67ffe41df326ae25e9e8092.avif?t=1770298492\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/257734b6a36d7d0005f8a61ec1e511d4.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/257734b6a36d7d0005f8a61ec1e511d4.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>The game's audio is a product of a compelling soundtrack and dynamic sound effects, to make your escape room experience the most realistic ever! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/bd6ff4a1c2d428242236a1abcc69dbf6.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/bd6ff4a1c2d428242236a1abcc69dbf6.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span>Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Japanese, and Russian.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>* The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1770298492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507540/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1770298492 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
